rubin elevation greater than 2 times ULN, aminotransferase elevations are greater than 8 times ULN, or aminotransferase elevations persist beyond 2 weeks.', 'Synergism', 'The use of bedaquiline with other potentially hepatotoxic agents should be avoided whenever possible (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/13304/', '', 'Capreomycin, Pyrazinamide, Rifamycin, Sulfamethoxazole, Rifapentine, Streptomycin, Trimethoprim, Rifampicin, Cycloserine, Rifabutin, Isoniazid, More', 'Acalabrutinib, Dacomitinib, Avapritinib, Selumetinib, Ibrutinib, Tivozanib, Zanubrutinib, Brigatinib, Ripretinib, Alpelisib, Ruxolitinib, More', 1767369485);
